      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, kept it garaged, and it's basically spotless inside and out. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you've gotta come see this beauty. It's ready for its next adventure and I'd love for it to go to a good home!",
