    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. The engine exhibits flawless VANOS operation and has undergone a comprehensive rod bearing service for preventative maintenance. The chassis remains structurally impeccable with a reinforced rear subframe and factory-spec suspension geometry, ensuring the tactile steering feedback and neutral handling balance the M-division is renowned for. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the interior retains its factory matte finish with no bolster wear. Mechanically synchronized and free of fluid seepage, this M3 is a turn-key investment for the discerning driver seeking naturally aspirated excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
